title: Pusha-T Live From Le Poisson Rouge
description: The chart-topping rapper pulled no punches during his performance at NPR Music's showcase in New York City on Wednesday night. Watch Pusha T perform a 17-song set that ranged from his work with Kanye West to his critically acclaimed new album, My Name Is My Name. "King Push" "Blocka" "Millions" "Hold On" "Suicide" "So Appalled" "Mercy" "Cook It Down" "My God" "Exodus 23:1" "I Don't Like" "New God Flow" "Pain" "Nosetalgia" "Sweet Serenade" "Numbers On The Board" "40 Acres"
